Translation.Text: Due to the fact that the project folder naming allows storing multiple projects in the same folder, the removal of project file data for one project causes the removal of file data for other projects in the same folder.
Remove project file data for this project and for any other project in the same folder, including the folder itself
No files/folders will be removed. You can remove project files manually.
